<%= render 'shared/mailers/header', title: "W9 Form Has Expired" %>

<p>Dear <%= @vendor.business_name %>,</p>

<%= render 'shared/mailers/status_box', status: :error, title: "Immediate Action Required", message: "Your W9 form has expired. We are unable to process any payments until you submit an updated form." %>

<p>To resume payment processing for voucher transactions, please submit an updated W9 form as soon as possible.</p>

<h3>How to Submit Your Updated W9:</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Download the current W9 form from the <a href="https://www.irs.gov/pub/irs-pdf/fw9.pdf">IRS website</a></li>
  <li>Complete and sign the form</li>
  <li>Log in to your vendor portal at <%= link_to "Vendor Portal", vendor_root_url(host: Rails.application.config.action_mailer.default_url_options[:host]) %></li>
  <li>Navigate to "Profile" and upload your new W9 form</li>
</ol>

<%= render 'shared/mailers/status_box', status: :info, title: "Payment Status" do %>
  <p>Any pending payments will be held until your new W9 form is received and approved. Once approved, all held payments will be processed according to our standard payment schedule.</p>
<% end %>

<p>If you have already submitted an updated W9 form, please disregard this message.</p>

<p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our vendor support team immediately.</p>

<%= render 'shared/mailers/footer' %>
